description:
Get Things Done with ProHelp - Your Local Services Marketplace

Find trusted professionals for any task or earn money with your skills. ProHelp connects you with your local community to get work done quickly, safely, and affordably.

Why ProHelp?

- Browse hundreds of local jobs across 20+ service categories
- Post tasks and receive proposals from qualified professionals
- Chat directly and securely within the app
- Check verified ratings and reviews before hiring
- Showcase your work with portfolio galleries
- Track all your jobs and applications in one place
- Available in English, Latvian, and Russian

For Job Posters:

Need help around the house? Looking for a professional service? Post your job in minutes:

- Describe your task with photos and details
- Set your estimated budget and location
- Receive proposals from qualified service providers
- Review portfolios, ratings, and previous work
- Chat to discuss details before hiring
- Approve the best proposal and get it done
- Leave a review to help the community

For Service Providers:

Turn your skills into income. Find opportunities that match your expertise:

- Browse jobs in your area and categories
- Filter by complexity, budget, and user rating
- Submit proposals with your estimate and timeline
- Showcase your best work in your portfolio gallery
- Chat with potential clients about project details
- Build your reputation with 5-star reviews
- Manage all applications from your dashboard

Popular Categories:

- Home Repairs & Maintenance
- Cleaning & Organizing
- Moving & Delivery
- Photography & Videography
- Tutoring & Lessons
- Event Services & Planning
- Personal Training & Fitness
- IT & Tech Support
- Beauty & Wellness
- And many more!

Key Features:

- Smart Search & Filters: Find exactly what you need with filters for complexity, location, user rating, and estimated budget.
- Secure In-App Chat: Communicate directly with clients or service providers. Share photos, discuss details, and negotiate terms safely.
- Ratings & Reviews: Build trust with verified reviews. Check provider ratings before hiring and grow your reputation with every completed job.
- Portfolio Galleries: Service providers can showcase their best work with photo galleries to attract more clients.
- Push Notifications: Never miss a new job opportunity, proposal, or message with instant notifications.
- Multilingual Support: Use ProHelp in English, Latvian, or Russian - perfect for diverse communities.
- Job Management Dashboard: Track posted jobs, submitted proposals, applications, and completed work all in one place.

How It Works:

Need Help?

1. Post your job with details and photos
2. Review proposals from local professionals
3. Check ratings and chat with providers
4. Approve a proposal and track progress
5. Rate your experience

Offering Services?

1. Browse jobs matching your skills
2. Submit detailed proposals
3. Chat with potential clients
4. Get approved and complete the work
5. Build your 5-star reputation

Safe & Secure:

Your safety matters. ProHelp uses phone verification, secure messaging, and community reviews to keep our marketplace trustworthy. Every user is verified, and all communications happen within the app.

Perfect For:

Whether you're a homeowner needing repairs, a business seeking services, or a professional looking to grow your client base - ProHelp brings your local community together.

Join Thousands of Users Today!

Download ProHelp now and discover how easy it is to find help or earn money in your community. Post your first job or start browsing opportunities - it's free to get started!

---

Questions? Contact us at support@prohelp.app
Follow us for tips and community highlights!

First OCTA mobile app in Latvia, that gives an opportunity to check validity terms of OCTA insurance, history and actual data about vehicle accidents. App allows you to switch on notifications about upcoming dates of OCTA validity terms, to find out your Bonus-Malus class. As well you can fill in Agreed Statement accident form, accept it and send information about an accident to your insurer. You can follow up information about an unlimited amount of vehicles in your vehicle park.
LTAB OCTA / Motor Insurers' Bureau of Latvia.

Pirmā mobilajām ierīcēm draudzīgā OCTA lietotne Latvijā, kurā iespējams uzzināt OCTA polises darbības termiņu, transportlīdzekļa negadījumu vēsturiskos un aktuālos datus. Lietotnē iespējams pieteikties atgādinājumiem par OCTA derīguma termiņu tuvošanos, noskaidrot savu Bonus-malus klasi. Tāpat varēsiet aizpildīt saskaņotā paziņojuma veidlapu, autentificēt to un negadījuma informāciju nosūtīt savam apdrošinātājam. Lietotne dod iespēju regulāri sekot līdzi neirobežota daudzuma transportlīdzekļu autoparkam.
LTAB OCTA / Latvijas Transportlīdzekļu apdrošinātāju birojs.

Izmantojot CSDD e-pakalpojumu mobilo aplikāciju Jūs jebkurā laikā un bez maksas varat uzzināt informāciju par sevi un savu transportlīdzekli, saņemt vienas dienas braukšanas atļauju, uzzināt reģistrēto velosipēdu datus. Ja esat jau reģistrējies kā CSDD e-pakalpojumu lietotājs, Jūs varat turpināt izmantot aplikāciju bez papildus reģistrācijas. 

CSDD aplikācija nodrošina: 
* Vadītāja apliecības dati: informācija par vadītāja apliecību, iegūtajām kategorijām, medicīnisko uzziņu 
* CSN pārkāpumi: informācija par personai spēkā esošajiem pārkāpumu uzskaites punktiem un neapmaksātiem naudas sodiem 
* Transportlīdzekļu dati: informācija par saviem, savā valdījumā un turējumā esošiem transportlīdzekļiem 
* Nodokļu kalkulators: transportlīdzekļa ekspluatācijas un uzņēmuma vieglo transportlīdzekļu nodokļa aprēķināšana 
* Tehniskās apskates dati: Latvijā reģistrēto transportlīdzekļu pēdējās tehniskās apskates dati 
* Maksas izziņas: informācija par transportlīdzekļiem un transportlīdzekļu vadītājiem
* Maksājumi: Apmaksāt CSDD pakalpojumus, nodevas un Ceļu satiksmes noteikumu pārkāpumu sodus, izmantojot elektroniskās maksājumu kartes
* Velosipēdi un to reģistrācija: Velosipēdu reģistrācija, datu apskate un labošana 
* Vienas dienas atļauja: vienas dienas atļaujas noformēšana, lai nokļūtu uz tehnisko apskati 
* Pieteikšanās eksāmeniem: Pieteikšanās uz kvalifikācijas teorijas un vadīšanas eksāmeniem
* Atgādinājumi: par vadītāja dokumentu, tehniskās apskates, medicīniskās uzziņas, OCTA u.c. termiņa beigām, sinhronizācija ar tālruņa kalendāru 
* Kontakti, informācija: CSDD sniegtie pakalpojumi, kontakti un darba laiki 
* Reģistrācijas datu maiņa: izmainīt reģistrācijas datus (e-pastu, paroli u.c.)
* Push paziņojumi: saņemt paziņojumus par (TA, OCTA, vadītāju dokumentu termiņiem, sodiem u.c.) arī tad ja aplikācija nav atvērta

Whether you’re connecting with your community for an upcoming activity or working with teammates on a project, Microsoft Teams helps bring people together so that they can get things done. It’s the only app that has communities, events, chats, channels, meetings, storage, tasks, and calendars in one place—so you can easily connect and manage access to information. Get your community, family, friends, or workmates together to accomplish tasks, share ideas, and make plans. Join audio and video calls in a secure setting, collaborate in documents, and store files and photos with built-in cloud storage. You can do it all in Microsoft Teams. 

Easily connect with anyone: 
• Skype is now part of Teams. Continue where you left off with your chats, calls and contacts in Microsoft Teams Free. 
• Meet securely with communities, teammates, family, or friends.
• Set up a meeting within seconds and invite anyone by sharing a link or calendar invite. 
• Chat 1-1 or to your entire community, @mention people in chats to get their attention. 
• Create a dedicated community to discuss specific topics and make plans*.
• Work closely and collaborate by keeping conversations organized by specific topics and projects with teams and channels.
• Video or audio call anyone directly in Teams or instantly convert a group chat to a call. 
• Use GIFs, emojis, and message animations to express yourself when words aren’t enough.
 
Accomplish plans and projects together: 
• Send photos and videos in chats to quickly and easily share important moments.
• Use cloud storage to access shared documents and files on the go. 
• Organize shared content in a community — events, photos, links, files —so you don’t have to waste time searching*. 
• Get the most out of your meetings by using screen share, whiteboard, or breakout in virtual rooms.
• Manage access to information and ensure the right people have access to the right info, even when people join and leave projects.
• Use task lists to stay on top of projects and plans - assign tasks, set due dates, and cross off items to keep everyone on the same page. 

Designed to give you peace of mind: 
• Securely collaborate with others while maintaining control over your data.
• Keep communities safe by allowing owners to remove inappropriate content or members*.
• Enterprise-level security and compliance you expect from Microsoft 365**. 

*Available when using Microsoft Teams with your Microsoft account.

**Commercial features of this app require a paid Microsoft 365 commercial subscription or a trial subscription of Microsoft Teams for work. If you’re not sure about your company’s subscription or the services you have access to, visit Office.com/Teams to learn more or contact your IT department. 

By downloading Teams, you agree to the license (see aka.ms/eulateamsmobile) and privacy terms (see aka.ms/privacy). For support or feedback, email us at mtiosapp@microsoft.com. EU Contract Summary: aka.ms/EUContractSummary

Smart-ID is the easiest, most convenient and safest way to authenticate yourself online – check your online bank account, access e-services and confirm transactions.

Smart-ID allows you to give signatures equal to handwritten signatures (except Basic level), which complies with EU regulations about qualified electronic signatures.

Smart-ID is currently available for:
-	Estonian, Latvian, Lithuanian residents
-	Estonian e-residents
-	Belgium residents


EASY 
Get started by downloading Smart-ID app.

Follow the steps in the app to confirm your identity and complete the registration process. Once you’ve done that, you’re good to go – no other confirmation needed! 

CONVENIENT
Your Smart-ID is always within an easy reach!

You can use Smart-ID in as many smart devices as you want and gain access to your online accounts across all of them any time, any place. Using Smart-ID is free and totally unlimited.

SAFE

Smart-ID app does not store your identity or PIN codes. The app is used for key management: it creates your private keys while account registration and later mediates authentication and signature requests. User identity is managed securely by the service provider. A technology has been used in this product for which Cybernetica AS has filed a patent application or a patent has been granted.

Try out Smart-ID, visit portal.smart-id.com!

About this app

Everything you love about WhatsApp plus built-in tools for business
WhatsApp Business is a free-to-download app with built-in tools to help you work smarter, build trust, and grow your business. 

You get  free calls* and free international messaging* plus business features to help you do more with conversations.

Download the app to get business benefits like these:

• Work smarter. Save time by letting the app do the work for you! Send customers automated quick replies and away messages so you never miss an opportunity. Use labels to quickly organize, filter, and find important conversations. Create a status to share an offer or news, and even take orders and payments** in-app to create a great customer experience. 


• Build relationships and trust. With a professional business profile on a secure platform,  you build credibility and trust with customers. Use the app to provide more responsive customer support and build long-term loyalty. Subscribe to Meta Verified*** to reinforce your authenticity.


• Sell more and grow. Get discovered, advertise, and make more valuable customer connections. Boost sales by sending targeted offers to customers; create ads that click to WhatsApp; showcase your product catalog; and give customers the convenience of in-app orders and payments.**

FAQs
Are all features free?
The app is free to download and use, with a mix of free and paid features.

Can I still use my personal WhatsApp?
Yes! As long as you have two different phone numbers, your business and personal accounts can live together on a single device.  

Can I transfer over my chat history?
Yes. When you set up the WhatsApp Business app, you can restore a backup from your WhatsApp account to transfer your messages, media, and contacts to your business account.

How many devices can I connect?
You can have a total of five web-based devices or mobile phones on your account (up to 10 if you subscribe to Meta Verified***). 

*Data charges may apply. Contact your provider for details.
**Not available in all markets
***Available soon globally

- Full support for Microsoft Word formats (.doc, .docx, .docm) along with .rtf and .txt.

Spreadsheets:

PDFs:

- Open, annotate, and manage PDF files with ease.
- Various reading modes for enhanced user experience.
- Access to tables of contents and annotations.
